cs.SI, cs.SD, cs.SY, cs.NI, cs.CE 

This paper deals with the spread of disease over a network, which is a topic that falls under the sub-categories of social networks (cs.SI), network science (cs.SD), and systems and control (cs.SY). The use of the SIR model and centrality measures also suggests that the paper could be classified under the sub-categories of networking and internet architecture (cs.NI) and computational engineering, finance, and science (cs.CE).
